  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997590/extras/0692d725ed4c9f964d996109ba889437.poster.avif?t=1750348569\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997590/extras/0692d725ed4c9f964d996109ba889437.webm?t=1750348569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997590/extras/0692d725ed4c9f964d996109ba889437.mp4?t=1750348569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >RETOOLED is a fast-paced single player FPS where you will have to use all of your weapons and abilities to come out victorious. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bunnyhop your way through increasingly complex arenas while facing a diverse and dynamic enemy lineup, designed to react to your actions and put your skills to the test. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997590/extras/e915d6125710ab4003efb07710033a9a.avif?t=1750348569\" width=700 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick your gear and unleash havoc! Complete challenges to expand your equipment and arsenal. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Weapons</strong> - 6 weapons, each one with an alt fire. Learn the different weapon combos to unlock your true potential. Orb launcher then Railgun? Who knows what will happen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Equipments</strong> - In need of a Jump Pack? Double Jump Boots? NO?! Well then.. select something that suits your playstyle. There are 5 different pieces of equipment. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Abilities</strong> - Make your clutch moves with your support, utility and offensive abilities.  Find your preference out of 13 different ones!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fast movement</strong> - Master your movement, dash, bash, or boost jump your way out of dangerous situtations. Bunnyhop your way through the levels (or for the bold: ROCKET JUMP!).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997590/extras/f6ddb83a28d8949eeee41425d39fd385.poster.avif?t=1750348569\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997590/extras/f6ddb83a28d8949eeee41425d39fd385.webm?t=1750348569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997590/extras/f6ddb83a28d8949eeee41425d39fd385.mp4?t=1750348569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997590/extras/5d20de864850932b8f0e32931b2faa7c.avif?t=1750348569\" width=700 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you achieve the title, LORD OF TOOLS? Wreck your enemies in style! Earn high score and climb the ranks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tales</strong> - Fight in epic Tales of Destruction after you finished the story. Maps are designed turn the fight up to 11! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>High score</strong> - Learn and earn the high score multipliers. Will you manage to combine the \"Bunny Trick\" with an \"Air Time\" multiplier while pulling off a \"Weapon Combo\"?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ranks</strong> - Rise in your rank as a NOVICE to the LORD OF TOOLS. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997590/extras/e39a2687e79c80b5cd1ea45529570e54.avif?t=1750348569\" width=700 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the biggest update for RETOOLED comes plenty of new stuff and improvements!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>10 Master levels</strong> - Re-experience the story with the new master level version.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New Tales level</strong> - Power station</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level updates</strong> - Improved lightning, graphics and level design.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Subtitles</strong> - English subtitles now exists!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Plenty more</strong> - VFX updates for weapons and etc, optimizations, bug fixes, balance changes, highscore rebalance, new challenges...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997590/extras/e34291cb9ab36ba157172be945c250f4.poster.avif?t=1750348569\" width=626 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997590/extras/e34291cb9ab36ba157172be945c250f4.webm?t=1750348569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997590/extras/e34291cb9ab36ba157172be945c250f4.mp4?t=1750348569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >RETOOLED is meant to be challenging, good luck and have fun wrecking your enemies!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997590/extras/0692d725ed4c9f964d996109ba889437.poster.avif?t=1750348569\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997590/extras/0692d725ed4c9f964d996109ba889437.webm?t=1750348569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997590/extras/0692d725ed4c9f964d996109ba889437.mp4?t=1750348569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >RETOOLED is a fast-paced single player FPS where you will have to use all of your weapons and abilities to come out victorious. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bunnyhop your way through increasingly complex arenas while facing a diverse and dynamic enemy lineup, designed to react to your actions and put your skills to the test. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1997590/extras/e915d6125710ab4003efb07710033a9a.avif?t=1750348569\" width=700 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick your gear and unleash havoc! Complete challenges to expand your equipment and arsenal. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Weapons</strong> - 6 weapons, each one with an alt fire. Learn the different weapon combos to unlock your true potential. Orb launcher then Railgun? Who knows what will happen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Equipments</strong> - In need of a Jump Pack? Double Jump Boots? NO?! Well then.. select something that suits your playstyle. There are 5 different pieces of equipment. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Abilities</strong> - Make your clutch moves 